data.description: $20,000 Price Improvement!  Fantastic 4 bedroom, 2 bath home with 2065 square feet conveniently located to Eastdale Mall, shops & restaurants!  In addition to having a NEW ROOF, NEW HVAC SYSTEM & NEW WATER HEATER, NEW PLUMBING in kitchen, laundry & bathrooms & NEW ELECTRICAL PANEL & NEW ELECTRICAL OUTLETS, the owner has updated the kitchen with granite countertops, stainless appliances, and new tile flooring.  Both bathrooms have been updated with new plumbing, new toilets, new vanities with granite countertops & tile tub surround!  Features a Spacious Living/Dining Room with wood burning fireplace; Laundry is located off the kitchen; Bedroom located downstairs has a walk in closet and access to the guest bathroom;  Upstairs you will find 2 additional guest bedrooms and an oversized master suite with sitting area that connects to the upstairs bathroom that also has access to the hallway!  Step outside to a HUGE back yard that is fully fenced and has a covered patio. Gorgeous bricked in mailbox with marble & granite that has secure keyed lockbox!
